  "detailed_description": "<strong>Paths of Fight: Samurai</strong> is an original hack'n'slash puzzle game that challenges you to find the correct path and kill all enemies in the fight.<br>Think wisely, plan your moves, slash enemies, and finish them with powerful combos.  <br>Play as a Samurai in a series of combats that require strategic and logical thinking to succeed. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287100/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1704981119\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287100/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1704981119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287100/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1704981119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Slash your enemies with each move.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287100/extras/e0a1115e64ead8ea89479761a1cfaf20.poster.avif?t=1704981119\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287100/extras/e0a1115e64ead8ea89479761a1cfaf20.webm?t=1704981119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287100/extras/e0a1115e64ead8ea89479761a1cfaf20.mp4?t=1704981119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Move wisely, cause each move counts</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287100/extras/76faca0ac0a59498daf76285f9bda91f.poster.avif?t=1704981119\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287100/extras/76faca0ac0a59498daf76285f9bda91f.webm?t=1704981119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287100/extras/76faca0ac0a59498daf76285f9bda91f.mp4?t=1704981119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Finish with style.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287100/extras/9f98d48b8fae03866828908779d9b201.poster.avif?t=1704981119\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287100/extras/9f98d48b8fae03866828908779d9b201.webm?t=1704981119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287100/extras/9f98d48b8fae03866828908779d9b201.mp4?t=1704981119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featuring:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Original mechanics</strong>. Move through the lines and find the correct path to kill all enemies.<br></li><li><strong>40+ hand-crafted levels</strong> with increasing complexity.<br></li><li><strong>Beautiful environments</strong> of Japan in the feudal era.<br></li><li><strong>Easy controls</strong>. Only mouse clicks.</li></ul>",
